WEBVTT

1
00:00:09.333 --> 00:00:10.000
Xi Shao

2
00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.100
Why are you here? I heard that Sibao is sick.

3
00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:12.666
Come and see

4
00:00:12.666 --> 00:00:13.933
Thank you for your concern

5
00:00:13.933 --> 00:00:15.100
I'm here now.

6
00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:16.000
You can leave now.

7
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:16.800
The child is sick.

8
00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:18.766
You don't even know how you became a mother

9
00:00:18.766 --> 00:00:21.266
It's not up to an outsider to take care of my family's affairs

10
00:00:21.266 --> 00:00:22.233
Please go out

11
00:00:22.366 --> 00:00:24.100
Otherwise your wife will be jealous again.

12
00:00:24.133 --> 00:00:26.100
It's not because I feel sorry for this child

13
00:00:30.733 --> 00:00:32.933
Do you still want to worry about this child?

14
00:00:32.933 --> 00:00:35.433
Forget it, since he's a kid of velvet paper

15
00:00:35.466 --> 00:00:36.900
I don't need to worry

16
00:00:38.366 --> 00:00:40.800
Miss Shang, how is my daughter?

17
00:00:40.866 --> 00:00:42.833
Your daughter's health is not good.

18
00:00:42.866 --> 00:00:44.933
She developed acute leukemia today

19
00:00:44.933 --> 00:00:45.966
How could this be?

20
00:00:45.966 --> 00:00:47.800
I remember reminding you before.

21
00:00:47.800 --> 00:00:49.300
Get you a 1 million

22
00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:50.133
Did you get it together?

23
00:00:50.133 --> 00:00:51.500
Immediate surgery is required

24
00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:54.400
Otherwise you can only plan for the worst

25
00:00:57.933 --> 00:00:59.266
Nice

26
00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:02.000
Why did you suddenly get sick?

27
00:01:19.266 --> 00:01:20.300
Hello, Mom.

28
00:01:20.300 --> 00:01:22.666
I gave you all my previous salary.

29
00:01:22.666 --> 00:01:24.133
How much do you have left now?

30
00:01:24.133 --> 00:01:26.266
I said before that I have no money.

31
00:01:26.266 --> 00:01:27.766
It's this time

32
00:01:27.933 --> 00:01:30.466
Are you going to die for the Four Treasures?

33
00:01:30.466 --> 00:01:31.200
You white-eyed wolf

34
00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:32.400
Just feel sorry for your daughter, right?

35
00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:34.666
Don't feel sorry for me, take all the money and keys to save him.

36
00:01:34.666 --> 00:01:35.600
What should I do?

37
00:01:35.600 --> 00:01:38.100
No money is no money mom

38
00:01:48.266 --> 00:01:50.766
Xia Lily heard that your daughter is sick.

39
00:01:50.766 --> 00:01:52.233
I will come here to help you.

